<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 20:07:53 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>哈马斯表示，美国关于加沙停火的新提议满足了内塔尼亚胡的新要求，阻碍了达成协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/hamas-new-u-s-proposal-accommodates-netanyahus-new-demands-prevents-deal/00000191-66d7-d3bf-a3b1-eff7abd30000</link><description>哈马斯在多哈周末峰会以来的首份官方声明中指责内塔尼亚胡“设定新条件来破坏谈判”，并补充说新要求不符合其释放安全囚犯的条件</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 19:07:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/hamas-new-u-s-proposal-accommodates-netanyahus-new-demands-prevents-deal/00000191-66d7-d3bf-a3b1-eff7abd30000</guid></item><item><title>美国国务卿布林肯抵达以色列，推动加沙协议恢复谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/u-s-secretary-of-state-blinken-arrives-in-israel-to-push-for-gaza-deal-as-talks-resume/00000191-66a0-d3bf-a3b1-efb7adde0000</link><description>布林肯将与以色列官员举行会议，试图就与哈马斯的关键争论点达成谅解，谈判代表继续在埃及和卡塔尔举行会议</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 18:28:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/u-s-secretary-of-state-blinken-arrives-in-israel-to-push-for-gaza-deal-as-talks-resume/00000191-66a0-d3bf-a3b1-efb7adde0000</guid></item><item><title>美国正在追捕以色列极右翼部长，他们对定居者的暴力表示欢迎</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-18/ty-article/.highlight/america-is-coming-for-israels-far-right-ministers-who-hail-settler-violence/00000191-65e6-dda8-af9b-65e6b4450000</link><description>定居者暴力持续不减的时间越长，后果就越严重，国际领导人采取自己的惩罚措施就越有道理</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 18:09:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-18/ty-article/.highlight/america-is-coming-for-israels-far-right-ministers-who-hail-settler-violence/00000191-65e6-dda8-af9b-65e6b4450000</guid></item><item><title>以色列保安人员在约旦河西岸袭击中被巴勒斯坦人杀害</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-security-guard-killed-by-palestinian-in-west-bank-attack/00000191-6687-d772-a9d5-6ebf47430000</link><description>袭击者用锤子将 38 岁的吉迪恩·佩里 (Gideon Perry) 打成致命伤，然后偷走了他的武器并驾车逃跑。以色列军队仍在追捕嫌疑人</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 17:41:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-security-guard-killed-by-palestinian-in-west-bank-attack/00000191-6687-d772-a9d5-6ebf47430000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国家检察官将领导对定居者袭击巴勒斯坦村庄事件的调查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/israels-state-prosecutor-to-lead-investigation-into-settler-attack-on-palestinian-village/00000191-6669-deb0-ab91-f7fd846f0000</link><description>在对吉特的突袭中，一名巴勒斯坦人被枪杀，但没有逮捕任何人，国防机构的初步调查表明，预备役士兵可能在现场袖手旁观</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 17:35:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/israels-state-prosecutor-to-lead-investigation-into-settler-attack-on-palestinian-village/00000191-6669-deb0-ab91-f7fd846f0000</guid></item><item><title>“我们之间有一堵冰墙”：罗宋汤地带的阿拉伯和犹太青少年结下了不解之缘</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/there-was-an-ice-wall-between-us-arab-and-jewish-teens-bond-in-the-borscht-belt/00000191-650d-d301-ad91-f57f9dfb0000</link><description>在卡茨基尔山度过一个夏天后，来自以色列的阿拉伯青少年回到了一个在战前很久就被种族隔离的动荡国家。组织者希望他们的对话能够产生影响</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 17:05:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/there-was-an-ice-wall-between-us-arab-and-jewish-teens-bond-in-the-borscht-belt/00000191-650d-d301-ad91-f57f9dfb0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 317 天：以色列国家检察官将领导对约旦河西岸定居者骚乱的调查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-317-israels-state-prosecutor-to-lead-probe-of-west-bank-settler-riot/00000191-6630-d398-a7f5-ff70f9370000</link><description>哈马斯消息人士告诉沙特日报《Al Sharq》，目前正在讨论的停火提案“完全违背”哈马斯 7 月同意的协议 ■ 总理内塔尼亚胡表示，以色列愿意在谈判中的某些问题上保持灵活性 ■ 美国国务卿布林肯抵达以色列，将于周一与内塔尼亚胡会面，讨论确保加沙停战的努力 ■ 这是战争开始 317 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 16:54:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-317-israels-state-prosecutor-to-lead-probe-of-west-bank-settler-riot/00000191-6630-d398-a7f5-ff70f9370000</guid></item><item><title>“他们是来杀人的”：以色列定居者袭击巴勒斯坦村庄后，当地人担心没有人来拯救他们</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/after-settler-attack-on-palestinian-village-locals-fear-theres-no-one-to-save-them/00000191-65d2-d3bf-a3b1-edf7aaa40000</link><description>周四，以色列定居者在约旦河西岸吉特村杀害了一名 23 岁男子，当地居民表示，这次袭击是一次精心策划的袭击，他们担心还会再次发生</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 15:27:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/after-settler-attack-on-palestinian-village-locals-fear-theres-no-one-to-save-them/00000191-65d2-d3bf-a3b1-edf7aaa40000</guid></item><item><title>报告：以色列在高级官员被杀之前破坏了真主党的通信网络</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/report-israel-breached-hezbollahs-communications-network-before-top-officials-killing/00000191-65f3-dda8-af9b-65f3cde50000</link><description>据《华尔街日报》报道，福阿德·舒克 (Fuad Shukr) 在以色列袭击导致他死亡之前接到电话，告诉他该去哪里</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 15:09:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/report-israel-breached-hezbollahs-communications-network-before-top-officials-killing/00000191-65f3-dda8-af9b-65f3cde50000</guid></item><item><title>《时代》杂志对内塔尼亚胡的采访进行了事实核查——他所说的并非全部都是真的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/time-fact-checked-their-interview-with-netanyahu-not-everything-he-said-was-true/00000191-654a-d772-a9d5-6ffe12090000</link><description>此次接受《时代周刊》采访是首相自10月7日以来第27次接受外国媒体采访，在接受该杂志工作人员核实后，他在采访中发表了一些虚假言论。</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 13:15:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/time-fact-checked-their-interview-with-netanyahu-not-everything-he-said-was-true/00000191-654a-d772-a9d5-6ffe12090000</guid></item><item><title>国防部消息人士称，警方拒绝调查试图渗透巴勒斯坦村庄的以色列人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/police-refused-to-probe-israeli-who-tried-to-infiltrate-palestinian-village-source-says/00000191-6450-d478-a99b-f77580fc0000</link><description>六名以色列人试图进入纳布卢斯以南的一个巴勒斯坦村庄，其中一些人戴着面具，但在以色列军队到达现场后逃离。此前，定居者上周袭击了约旦河西岸的一个巴勒斯坦村庄，造成一人死亡</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 09:38:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/police-refused-to-probe-israeli-who-tried-to-infiltrate-palestinian-village-source-says/00000191-6450-d478-a99b-f77580fc0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列窃听定居者、犹太学院学生和清真寺</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-israeli-artist-eavesdropping-on-settlers-yeshiva-students-and-mosques/00000191-5c63-dd29-a7f3-7d6bdb240000</link><description>此外，一家传奇的特拉维夫书店从拉宾广场地区搬到了弗洛伦丁，而耶路撒冷的木偶戏剧节也将试图缓解战争的影响</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 07:30:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-israeli-artist-eavesdropping-on-settlers-yeshiva-students-and-mosques/00000191-5c63-dd29-a7f3-7d6bdb240000</guid></item><item><title>现在是拜登的表演：他能引导以色列和哈马斯达成加沙协议吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/biden-is-trying-to-talk-a-deal-into-existence-but-a-breakthrough-isnt-yet-on-the-horizon/00000191-61ab-d993-a5d7-ebef1ef70000</link><description>美国总统正试图营造积极情绪，希望实现加沙停火并挫败伊朗袭击，但相关人士却不那么乐观 ■ 即使没有全面战争，以色列北部居民的生活也是难以忍受的与真主党合作 ■ 右翼对约旦河西岸致命定居者骚乱的谴责远没有令人信服</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 03:01:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/biden-is-trying-to-talk-a-deal-into-existence-but-a-breakthrough-isnt-yet-on-the-horizon/00000191-61ab-d993-a5d7-ebef1ef70000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯表示，美国关于加沙停火的新提议满足了内塔尼亚胡的新要求，阻碍了达成协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article-live/two-hamas-members-killed-in-idf-airstrike-in-west-bank-israel-attacks-targets-in-lebanon/00000191-635f-dd29-a7f3-675f3bac0000</link><description>以色列国防军正在追捕在约旦河西岸杀害以色列保安人员的袭击者。 ■ 以色列国防军士兵在加沙被火箭弹重伤。 ■ 内塔尼亚胡：我们在某些事情上不能保持灵活性。军事和外交压力是释放人质的途径 ■ 内塔尼亚胡和布林肯将于周一在耶路撒冷总理办公室会面</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 02:57:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article-live/two-hamas-members-killed-in-idf-airstrike-in-west-bank-israel-attacks-targets-in-lebanon/00000191-635f-dd29-a7f3-675f3bac0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在加沙南部发布更多撤离令，缩小人道主义区</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-issues-more-evacuation-orders-in-south-gaza-shrinking-safe-zone/00000191-61fe-dd29-a7f3-65ff11b10000</link><description>联合国表示，大多数加沙人已经流离失所，其中许多人被迫多次撤离，而且在整个战争期间，约 84% 的加沙地区已被疏散</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 21:53:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-issues-more-evacuation-orders-in-south-gaza-shrinking-safe-zone/00000191-61fe-dd29-a7f3-65ff11b10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队命名两名在加沙战斗中丧生的预备役军人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-names-two-reservists-killed-in-gaza-fighting/00000191-61fa-d1d3-a5f7-71fe32c20000</link><description>约塔姆·伊扎克·佩莱德（Yotam Itzhak Peled）军官（后任）和莫迪凯·约瑟夫·本·肖姆（Mordechai Yosef Ben Shoam）少校（后任）均 34 岁，在加沙中部被爆炸装置炸死</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 21:26:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-names-two-reservists-killed-in-gaza-fighting/00000191-61fa-d1d3-a5f7-71fe32c20000</guid></item><item><title>卡塔尔让伊朗了解情况，以色列距离释放人质协议又近了一步</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-team-cautiously-optimistic-after-hostage-release-talks-in-doha-netanyahu-says/00000191-61d8-d1d3-a5f7-71fe0eb50000</link><description>以色列消息人士澄清说，尽管多哈峰会在推进部分计划方面取得了“重大进展”，但仍在等待哈马斯的回应。正在努力安排周三在开罗举行的另一轮会谈</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 20:20:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-team-cautiously-optimistic-after-hostage-release-talks-in-doha-netanyahu-says/00000191-61d8-d1d3-a5f7-71fe0eb50000</guid></item><item><title>在谈判中持谨慎乐观态度的情况下，全国各地的以色列人呼吁达成释放人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-17/ty-article/.premium/amid-cautious-optimism-in-talks-israelis-across-the-country-call-for-a-hostage-deal/00000191-60d0-d017-abd9-f9f484c70000</link><description>“你得到了以色列人民的全力支持。人质的兄弟说：“不要羞于做出最道德、最犹太化的决定，把他们带回家。”</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 17:41:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-17/ty-article/.premium/amid-cautious-optimism-in-talks-israelis-across-the-country-call-for-a-hostage-deal/00000191-60d0-d017-abd9-f9f484c70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 316 天：加沙卫生官员称以色列国防军袭击导致加沙地带中部 17 人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-316-gaza-health-officials-say-idf-strike-kills-17-in-central-strip/00000191-6146-d478-a99b-f77759c00000</link><description>巴勒斯坦人报告以色列对加沙中部的袭击造成 17 人死亡、数十人受伤 ■ 黎巴嫩卫生部：以色列袭击造成 10 人死亡；以色列国防军：袭击真主党武器储存设施 ■ 拜登官员：停火/人质协议谈判“现已进入最后阶段”。 ■ 以色列调查发现，以色列国防军士兵在周四的约旦河西岸定居者袭击中袖手旁观 ■ 以下是战争开始 316 天后您需要了解的信息</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 17:14:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-316-gaza-health-officials-say-idf-strike-kills-17-in-central-strip/00000191-6146-d478-a99b-f77759c00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列对黎巴嫩的袭击造成十人死亡；真主党火箭弹袭击导致两名以色列国防军士兵受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-17/ty-article/ten-killed-in-israeli-strike-in-lebanon-hezbollah-rocket-barrage-wounds-two-idf-soldiers/00000191-6087-d1d3-a5f7-70ff66080000</link><description>以色列军队报告称，它袭击了黎巴嫩南部的真主党武器储存设施以及其他与恐怖活动有关的地点。当地卫生部门表示，受害者包括一名母亲和她的两个孩子</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 15:30:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-17/ty-article/ten-killed-in-israeli-strike-in-lebanon-hezbollah-rocket-barrage-wounds-two-idf-soldiers/00000191-6087-d1d3-a5f7-70ff66080000</guid></item></channel></rss>